verbose_text: The expression of the WT luciferase reporter in HeLa cells was significantly repressed by miR-9 precursor mimics (pre-miR-9) compared to scrambled precursors (pre-Scr), while the expression of the mutated luciferase reporter was not significantly affected, confirming the direct repression by miR-9 (XREF_FIG A).
evidence: expression of the WT luciferase reporter
